{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ssh"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Spooktacular waits for the VM to boot, resolves its IP"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"address, connects via SSH, and runs your script remotely."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is the most flexible mode — you get real-time output"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"streaming and an interactive connection."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Best for:"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" Cloned VMs where the base image has SSH"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(Remote Login) enabled. Development workflows where you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to see output as it runs."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires:"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" Remote Login (SSH) enabled in the guest.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The base image must have an SSH user and either password","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or key-based authentication configured.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Executes the script over SSH after the VM boots."}],"metadata":{"title":"ProvisioningMode.ssh","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"roleHeading":"Case","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ssh","kind":"identif